  "detailed_description": "<h1>Dark Light's horror game</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Perform the ritual with the doll, and you'll become happy.】</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406970/extras/1e894063a2e58c765fd15f46d9e1af96.avif?t=1685970104\" width=200 height=66 /></span><br>Lucy bought an exquisite large doll at a low price.<br>The doll comes with instructions in the package - \"Doll's Happiness Magic\".<br>She'll become happy if she combs its hair and talks to it!<br>Lucy follows the instructions cheerfully.<br>However, it's not a happy life waiting for her in the future.<br>It's an endless nightmare...<br><br>★A visual novel with two endings<br>★A story of more than 4000 words<br>★Doll animated charecter*1<br>★Monster animated CG*1, ending CG*2<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406970/extras/26a99768b53d474a6bbc6af9d719d822.avif?t=1685970104\" width=200 height=66 /></span><br>★Jump scare<br>★Frightening guts images<br>★Depressing and dark description<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406970/extras/3de9e25539eb5a2ca74d42a609a01b13.avif?t=1685970104\" width=200 height=66 /></span><br>Hello, I'm Can-Yue (C.moon), a Taiwanese.<br>I'm running an independent game studio - Dark Light Studio, developing indie games.(｡・ω・｡)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406970/extras/1f7f9c0da1e5ab143093c6fd8eb52ef2.poster.avif?t=1685970104\" width=222 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406970/extras/1f7f9c0da1e5ab143093c6fd8eb52ef2.webm?t=1685970104\" type=\"video/webm